ITV.Tour.de.France.2014.Stage.9.Highlights.PDTV.x264-NX

Sunday 13th July 2014 ITV4
7pm to 8pm Highlights

Stage nine highlights which is a bumpy 170km between Gerardmer and Mulhouse with climbs typical of the Vosges region, being long rather than particularly steep. With six of them on route, today it looks like a perfect day for a breakaway. Presented by Gary Imlach with analysis from Chris Boardman, commentary by Phil Liggett and Paul Sherwen with Ned Boulting the reporter at the roadside.
